OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777648266
OL,3,CPlane crashed during spin stunt,
OL,4,Creport finds
OL,6,FTwo men died when the plane they were
OL,7,Fin crashed during an aerobatic stunt,
OL,8,Finvestigators have said.
OL,10,FMatthew Bird, 21, and his 24-year-old
OL,11,Fpassenger Oliver Dawes were in a two-
OL,12,Fseater Cessna light aircraft, which
OL,13,Fcame down at Thorganby, near Selby,
OL,14,FNorth Yorkshire, on 28 July last year.
OL,16,FThe Air Accidents Investigation Branch
OL,17,F(AAIB) said the plane was flying north
OL,18,Fof Breighton Airfield when it entered
OL,19,Fa left hand spin.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G1/6
