CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777648266
OL,3,CPlane crashed during spin stunt,
OL,4,Creport finds
OL,6,FAttempts to correct the manoeuvre
OL,7,Ffailed and the aircraft remained in a
OL,8,Fspin until it hit the ground.
OL,10,FThe AAIB said: "The pilot was newly
OL,11,Frated for aerobatic flying, and it was
OL,12,Flikely that the spin recovery
OL,13,Ftechnique had not yet become a skill-
OL,14,Fbased response that he could apply
OL,15,Feffectively even when surprised."
OL,17,FThe report said Mr Bird had started
OL,18,Fflying in January 2021 and had logged
OL,19,F153 hours of flying.
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G2/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
