FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36703
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777648266
OL,3,CPlane crashed during spin stunt,
OL,4,Creport finds
OL,6,FVideo recordings from inside the
OL,7,Fcockpit showed the pilot performing
OL,8,Fmanoeuvres from over 5,000ft.
OL,10,FAs the plane started to spin, the two
OL,11,Fmen counted to three, referencing the
OL,12,Fnumber of spins, before Mr Bird
OL,13,Fattempted to recover.
OL,15,FA mayday call was issued, saying the
OL,16,Faircraft was "in an uncontrolled spin".
OL,18,FIt descended at around 5,700ft a
OL,19,Fminute.
OL,26,@xD@NOUxD@fO]
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G3/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
