OL,24,ANext Page BYorks News CReg TV FThis Day
FL,368,360,260,120,000,100
PN,36704
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777648266
OL,3,CPlane crashed during spin stunt,
OL,4,Creport finds
OL,6,FAn examination of the aircraft by the
OL,7,FAAIB found no pre-existing failures
OL,8,Fwhich would have affected its function.
OL,10,FMr Bird's instructors described him as
OL,11,Fa particularly competent pilot with an
OL,12,Fenthusiastic and conscientious
OL,13,Fattitude to flying.
OL,15,FThe report added: "The accident
OL,16,Fhighlighted how unexpectedly
OL,17,Fchallenging it can be to recover from
OL,18,Fmultiple-turn spins."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G4/6
OL,2,W,.!+.!/*%/*%,.!/*%/*%/"-$T,,,,,,,,,,,,,
