PN,36705
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F367A1777648266
OL,3,CPlane crashed during spin stunt,
OL,4,Creport finds
OL,6,FThe report said the crash had prompted
OL,7,Fthe Civil Aviation Authority (CAA) to
OL,8,Fspeak to flying schools about safety
OL,9,Faround performing spin manoeuvres.
OL,11,FThe AAIB said: "Following this
OL,12,Faccident, the CAA intended to promote
OL,13,Fto flying schools its safety sense
OL,14,Fleaflet and video about spin awareness
OL,15,Fand the use of parachutes."
OL,1,Woz5~k4{$z%~s1z5jw=hw1         G5/6
